lead_paragraph: Around the turn of the last century, the steel magnate Andrew Carnegie paid to build 1,689 libraries across the United States. Many are still in use, celebrated as monumental works of philanthropy.

abstract: A slew of opponents of the tax are running in the city’s election Tuesday and beverage industry has spent more than $600,000 on ads aiming to turn public opinion against it.

lead_paragraph: PHILADELPHIA — Jeff Foster, 58, a retired security guard with an abiding sweet tooth and a generous paunch, scowled as he considered the cornucopia of refrigerated soft drinks at his local convenience store.

abstract: The moves could hamstring the Chinese tech giant, escalating a cold war between China and the United States over technology and trade.
snippet: The moves could hamstring the Chinese tech giant, escalating a cold war between China and the United States over technology and trade.
lead_paragraph: LONDON — The Chinese technology giant Huawei on Monday began to feel the painful ripple effects of a Trump administration order that effectively bars American firms from selling components and software to the company, ramping up a cold war between the two countries over technology and trade.

abstract: The understated late bloomer called the final round “stressful,” but he fought through windy conditions to hold off a charge by Dustin Johnson.
snippet: The understated late bloomer called the final round “stressful,” but he fought through windy conditions to hold off a charge by Dustin Johnson.
lead_paragraph: FARMINGDALE, N.Y. — Brooks Koepka’s heart rate, he said Saturday night, probably would not vary much whether he was sitting on the couch watching the 101st P.G.A. Championship or sizing up a putt on Bethpage Black’s 72nd green to win it.

abstract: Tsai, the new owner of the Liberty and part owner of the Nets, has made a fortune as a founder of the Chinese e-commerce giant Alibaba Group. He’s hoping his skills can produce needed revenue for the W.N.B.A.

lead_paragraph: The Liberty will begin their season against the Indiana Fever at Westchester County Center on Friday, but the new owner, Joe Tsai, does not plan to have the team’s sojourn north of New York City continue much longer.

abstract: Faith, like feminism, sets high expectations for husbands.
snippet: Faith, like feminism, sets high expectations for husbands.
lead_paragraph: “Blue” marriages are better — or at least that is the conventional wisdom. Couples who live according to egalitarian values, sharing domestic responsibilities like housework and cooking, have long been seen as superior by most academics, journalists and public intellectuals engaged in the national conversation about the American family.
